1. What this Script Does
This script:
✅ Reads document IDs from a CSV file
✅ Authenticates to Veeva Vault
✅ Gets a Session ID
✅ Downloads a specific rendition of each document
✅ Saves files locally
✅ Creates a success/failure log
In simple language:
Plain TextCSV File   ↓Login to Vault   ↓Read Document IDs   ↓Download PDF/Viewable Rendition   ↓Save Files   ↓Create Log ReportShow more lines

